ContentDesc_Zenit der Götter - Tsukuyomi: Upon hearing of your final encounter with Yotsuyu─and the primal to whom she surrendered her will─the wandering minstrel composes a tanka tinged with sorrow. Had Yotsuyu been born in a different time, a different place, would she have lived a simple life unsullied by acts of violence and cruelty? Or were the seeds of villainy always there, their growth merely hastened by circumstance? These questions bring to mind Tsukuyomi's overwhelming malice, your memories now suffused by the tragedy of the minstrel's verse...
QuestName_Songs in the Key of Kugane: Songs in the Key of Kugane
instancecontenttextdata_ids_19500_Text: Oh...it's going to be a long night.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_19501_Text: Let's share the torment, shall we...?
instancecontenttextdata_ids_19503_Text: Struggle all you wish─I encourage it! Your death will be all the sweeter...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_19505_Text: Worthless excuse for a daughter. You're nothing but trouble.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_19506_Text: A font of misery, that's what you are!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_19507_Text: Fight like your life depends on it, dear sister. You wouldn't want to disappoint me...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_19508_Text: If it isn't the cold-blooded little worm. Always crawling through my rotten heart.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_19509_Text: Your pitiful fortunes can bring you no lower...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_19511_Text: Why...? You have no place here...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_19512_Text: Perhaps... But it is too late for me. There can be no redemption.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_19514_Text: In darkness blooms the spider lily...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_19515_Text: From mortal husk I rise anew!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_19516_Text: Suffused with night, I shall prevail!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_19517_Text: In moonlight's chill, shine petals pale...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_19518_Text: In sunless gloom, black tendrils trail...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_19519_Text: Rising moon! A light without warmth, stark and uncaring!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_19520_Text: Reaping crescent! A sweeping doom, striking from darkness!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_19521_Text: No. No... Not yet. Not. Yet.
instancecontenttextdata_ids_19522_Text: Yes, my dearest parents. I was the bane of your existence unto the very end!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_19524_Text: This is far from over! My bloodied hands have much left to accomplish!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_19525_Text: A nightbloom shall flower here upon the site of my demise...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_19527_Text: You have come to deliver judgment for my failure? Cut me down, then. Surely it is a simple task!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_19529_Text: You must survive, Tsuyu! The kami spared us, and we cannot repay that boon in death!
instancecontenttextdata_ids_19531_Text: Am I sunk to my lowest, then...?
instancecontenttextdata_ids_19532_Text: ...Ah. I understand. It feeds on my spite. On my suffering...
instancecontenttextdata_ids_19533_Text: Come forth, shades of the dead! Curse my name! Strike my body! Fill my soul with blackest malice!
